data.description: Welcome to your dream home with backyard views! This two-story residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and energy efficiency. Here's a glimpse of what this property has to offer:  This home boasts a thoughtfully designed two-story floor plan. Upstairs, discover three bedrooms and two bathrooms, providing space for family or guests. Meanwhile, the convenience of a downstairs bedroom and bathroom adds flexibility to the living arrangements.  The interior has been recently enhanced with new paint and upgraded flooring throughout, creating a modern and inviting atmosphere. Plush new carpet adds a touch of luxury to the bedrooms, while the new flooring provides a sleek and easy-to-maintain surface in some high-traffic areas.  The family room, complete with a cozy fireplace, is the heart of the home. Perfect for chilly evenings, it offers a warm and inviting space for gatherings or quiet moments by the fire. New ceiling fans have been installed to ensure comfort and energy efficiency year-round.  The property offers more than just a beautiful interior. A large backyard provides endless possibilities for outdoor activities, and a convenient shed offers extra storage space. The potential for RV parking adds practicality for those with recreational vehicles, ensuring that all your lifestyle needs are met.  This home is equipped with leased solar panels, a forward-thinking investment that not only contributes to a greener planet but also results in potential savings on your energy bills.    Don't miss the chance to make this exceptional property your own. Schedule a viewing today and experience the perfect blend of comfort, style, and eco-friendly living!
